org.youscope.common.table

Interface TableProducer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AutoFocusJob, CellDetectionAddon, CellDetectionJob, ControllerJob, DropletMicrofluidicJob, FluigentJob, NemesysJob, StatisticsJob

    public interface TableProducer
extends java.rmi.Remote
    Indicates that a given measurement component produces table data, and allows to add a listener to obtain produced data.
    Author:
    Moritz Lang
